item.title: CVE-2022-28792|2024-08-03T06:03:52.776Z -- samsung%20mobile -- gear%20iconx%20pc%20manager
item.description: DLL hijacking vulnerability in Gear IconX PC Manager prior to version 2.1.220405.51 allows attacker to execute arbitrary code. The patch adds proper absolute path to prevent dll hijacking.
